Package my.uum

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    App
    This class is to display the students' data that is divided into two parts, which are submitted and not submitted the Github account.
    dbResult
    This class is to display the students' data that is stored in the database with a certain format.
    GetGithubLink
    This class is to get all students' data who have submitted the github account from the url link and store into the database "GithubAccount".
    GetStudentList
    This class is to get all students' data in this Real-Time Programming class from the url link and store into the database "StudentList".
    StudentData
    This class is to set and get the students' data (matric, name, github link).
